{"tid":2196852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國宣稱塔利班若能維持和平 阿富汗將獲「可觀投資」","createTime":"2020-09-10T07:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T08:19:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"da7241ac5cc0a3890083cad170ff30bfb87d7f3a","tid":2196852,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"中國宣稱塔利班若能維持和平 阿富汗將獲「可觀投資」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287262&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=6d6d2bc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287262&h=b96acf2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287262</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕與阿富汗塔利班（Taliban）民兵組織熟悉的2名巴基斯坦消息來源近期表示，中國方面提出方案，稱如若塔利班能夠保證阿富汗在美軍撤出後「維持和平」，中國就會為阿富汗修建「公路網」，重整阿富汗經濟，不排除持續投資後續能源發展，以換取未來進口石油和天然氣的渠道。<br />\n<br />\n據《金融時報中文網》報導，巴基斯坦西南部俾路支省（Balochistan）部落首領透露，北京在過去3個月的會談中，提出將對阿富汗「能源和基礎設施項目進行可觀投資」，中方聲稱只要塔利班維護和平，中國的投資就會從修建公路開始，再來就會朝能源發展，例如發電，並透過阿富汗從中亞地區進口石油和天然氣。<br />\n<br />\n文中指出，俾路支省另外1位部落首領則透露，中國的承諾是要修建連結阿富汗主要城市的高速公路，以全國「公路網」為提案，而巴基斯坦外交部消息來源亦證實，從美國總統川普決定撤軍後，中國方面就不斷與塔利班代表會談。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡安全專家多爾西（James Dorsey）對此表示，針對阿富汗問題，中國似乎在為未來鋪路，更指出中國隊與其接壤國家展現出濃厚興趣，而阿富汗便是其中一國。巴基斯坦1名前情報員指出，中國一直敦促塔利班看到阿富汗經濟重整的好處，而塔利班似乎也理解了這件事。"},{"pid":"69d18c271dcbdd261fcb21321667bce26c3e339b","tid":2196852,"uid":33456,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"得罪穆斯林想用錢收賣返對家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf26423732d6a5ff5ff64b3b7bccaa8d213a087f","tid":2196852,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"信中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75fe96a67628a1c69fed66af0dc45c71073c31a","tid":2196852,"uid":150609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"一帶死路d 項目咪判返比自己友cap水 仲撚有人信你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c8048c9b9edf3e2c0f78999482b2ce273c4d9f","tid":2196852,"uid":281437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"救快必<br />\n要向法庭提供真實証據<br />\n寫「是特首的言行令我憎惡政府」在紙或布上<br />\n日日貼在手袋，背包上，帶出街<br />\n「是警方的言行⋯⋯⋯」<br />\n大家只需寫出真相就得"},{"pid":"0f992dce4ce9f7ab0c501ab5940e2f8b3a2ef453","tid":2196852,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:59:08.000Z","msg":"FT喎<br />\nreport得去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a8b950a1c24b08ae1f4e0e4212733e1d596e7a","tid":2196852,"uid":274996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"中共迫伊斯蘭食豬肉又拆清真寺，辱真主咁都忍？"},{"pid":"7b561745365a1ac535b5735202d08ea044f38184","tid":2196852,"uid":36162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"應該做，值得做，快啲做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中国係外交上俾包圍，係時候向西突破!!!<br />\n...<br />\n..<br />\n.<br />\n睇吓最後邊個俾人起尾注<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe50695b1fb5ec1e5bd219a6cfec65adfda87e0","tid":2196852,"uid":29188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"面對一個軍閥混戰嘅國家，竟然妄想收買其中一枝軍閥就可以保障全國投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f